casebody.data: JOHN RODNEY, Administrator d. b. n. of Luke Shields, v. WILLIAM SHANKLAND, Executor of Mary Neill, who was Executrix of Henry Neill, and ELIZABETH WRIGHT and FRETWELL WRIGHT, Executors of Peter F. Wright, and DANIEL RODNEY, Administrator of Henry Fisher. Court of Chancery. Sussex. July 24, 1818. Ridgely’s Notebook II, 180. [NO OPINION]
